org.lwjgl.ovr

Class OVRPoseStatef

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lwjgl.system.PointerWrapper
      • org.lwjgl.system.Struct
        • org.lwjgl.ovr.OVRPoseStatef
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Pointer

    public class OVRPoseStatef
extends Struct
    A full pose (rigid body) configuration with first and second derivatives.

    Body refers to any object for which ovrPoseStatef is providing data. It can be the HMD, Touch controller, camera or something else. The context depends on the usage of the struct.

    ovrPoseStatef members

    MemberTypeDescription
    ThePoseovrPosefposition and orientation
    AngularVelocityovrVector3fangular velocity in radians per second
    LinearVelocityovrVector3fvelocity in meters per second
    AngularAccelerationovrVector3fangular acceleration in radians per second per second
    LinearAccelerationovrVector3facceleration in meters per second per second
    TimeInSecondsdoubleabsolute time of this state sample
